Paper: hep-th/9810216

Date: 1998-10-27

Title: Exact BPS monopole solution in a self-dual background

Authors: Choonkyu Lee and Q-Han Park

Comments: 10 pages

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B449 (1999) 223-229

An exact one monopole solution in a uniform self-dual background field isobtained in the BPS limit of the SU(2) Yang-Mills-Higgs theory by using theinverse scattering method.